import { InfoWrapper, Form, Button, Label, Text } from "./Searchbar.styled"

export const Searchbar = ({ value, onChange }) => {

	return (
		<InfoWrapper className="searchbar">
			<Form className="form">
				<Button type="submit" className="button">
					<Label className="button-label">Search</Label>
				</Button>

				<Text
					className="input"
					type="text"
					autocomplete="off"
					autofocus
					placeholder="Search images and photos"
					value={value}
					onChange={onChange}
				/>
			</Form>
		</InfoWrapper>
	)
}
